title: Ep. #16 | DAY6, CIX, PUNCHNELLO, and RM
description:
Daebak Fam! DAY6 is back with “Time of Our Life”, CIX officially debuts with “Movie Star” and Punchnello releases a new single with Sam Kim “23”. Eric reacts to “Seoul Town Road ft. RM” by Lil Nas X, talks about his body falling apart, and tries his best to get an oat milk sponsorship for @daebakshow (pls help us). If you enjoyed this episode, make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Soundcloud, and YouTube! You can catch this full video of Eric recording this week’s episode surrounded by cactus and succulents in our brand new space. Which of your friends are missing out on this show? Tag away. Enjoy :) #day6 #timeofourlife #CIX #moviestar #Punchnello #SamKim #RM #LilNasX #SeoulTownRoad #EricNam #Daebakshow #Kpop
